# Script
#     rhoReactingBuoyantFoam
#
# Description
#     Script to inform the user that rhoReactingBuoyantFoam has been rename
#     buoyantReactingFoam
#
#------------------------------------------------------------------------------

cat << EOF

The rhoReactingBuoyantFoam solver has been renamed buoyantReactingFoam, and has
been extended so that it can also be run with psi-based thermodynamic models.

Any case that was previously executed using rhoReactingBuoyantFoam can now be
run with buoyantReactingFoam without modification.

EOF

